room_title: Escape room "Broke, Broker, Broken" by The Escape Artist KC in Kansas City
room_address: 408 B. East 18th St. Kansas City, MO 64108
room_description: Your team of private detectives has been hired to investigate a case of corporate embezzlement. Matt Steele went missing along with over 6.2 million dollars in company funds and the deeds to a lot of prime real estate. This starts out just like any other case, but something just doesn't feel right...
